-- Botswana Appoints Madzima as Acting Head of Financial Intelligence Agency
-- B y   J e r r y   B u n g u
-- 2010-11-03T17:00:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-03/botswana-appoints-madzima-as-acting-head-of-financial-intelligence-agency.html
Botswana appointed Jackson Madzima as
acting director of an agency that will fight crimes such as
money laundering, Finance and Development Planning Minister
Kenneth Matambo said.  The Financial Intelligence Agency will be fully operational
in the next fiscal year and the post of director has been
advertized, Matambo told reporters today in Gaborone, the
capital.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jerry Bungu in Gaborone at 
